koohiiStory1: Hunter-gathers, searching all along the ground for food. They never look up and see the Turkeys that have gathered on top of the trees to hide. Those were some smart turkeys!
koohiiStory2: Gather the turkeys for Thanksgiving. Gather the trees for Christmas. In that order...
